<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٤١٩٦ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْنَا الثَّوْرِيَّ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«هَذَا أَحْسَنُ الْبُيُوعِ عِنْدَنَا»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>